snippet.title: Best VGM 1101 - Pokemon Mystery Dungeon : Explorers of Sky - Temporal Tower
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1381 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8SJl4mELFMM
Best VGM 2366 - https://youtu.be/Chg7BqkgPjY

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Pokemon Mystery Dungeon : Explorers of Time / Darkness / Sky (2007)
Temporal Tower
Arata Iiyoshi & Atsuhiro Ishizuna
